block content
  section.hero
    .hero-body
      .content.has-text-centered
        h1
          strong Software Quality Consulting
        h2 3 Steps to Reliable Software
  section
    .container
      .columns
        .column.is-third
          .content
            h3 Strategy
            p.
              Together, we can devise a long-term strategy to focus your software
              development efforts on creating the most reliable and safe software.
              This will contain:
            h4 Approach
            ol
              li Find the right tools and approach
              li Perform Risk Analysis
              li Developer Training
        .column.is-third
          .content
            h3 Development
            p.
              Using the latest state of the art tools and techniques, I will
              implement safe and secure software. My background in IoT and Web
              Applications allows me to empower companies to solve their specific
              needs.
            h4 Areas of Expertise
            ul
              li Protocol Implementation
              li Transaction Processing
              li Message Queueing
        .column.is-third
          .content
            h3 Testing and Validation
            p.
              Cutting edge methods such as theorem proving or property based testing
              allow me to test, verify and validate the functionality of your
              software to an unprecedented degree of certainty.
            h4 Methods
            ul
              li White/Black-Box Testing
              li Property Based Testing
              li Theorem Proving
